@NODE History

V0.5:  it looks to be great :)
       now display the size of unpacked files in archives (in bytes)
       bug fix: can now choose the same archive 2 time in a row (i forget to reset
                a little variable... it's very bizarre because this bug appear only
                in V0.49, and only with LHA/LZX archives ...
       Enforcer Hit remove when showing XADmaster.library version in the menu:
       InStr(buf,$0D,0) is bad, InStr(buf,'$0D',0) is good ! 

V0.49: beta version (pre 0.5), (intern release)
       Now use XADmaster.library
       Little bug(?) corrected: 
          can't work if started from Cli: i forget to change the path in the 
          source ("wb:utils/arc" instead of "PROGDIR:" )

V0.41: use untgz but i lost the source ... no aminet release.

V0.4:  i lost the source too :(
       Now can UnZip!
       Added "GSREQF_CENTERTEXT" flag in About request
       catalogs recompiled

V0.33: Deutsch catalog added (thanks Christian Kersting)
       Bug fix: Add "pattern" in Reqtools requester
                Double click now work in requester too !
                Can NOW display archived'files with "spaced name" 
                  (can't in V0.32)

V0.32: Bug fix: Can now unarc and display archived'files with "spaced name"
                i forget to put boring requesters in V0.31 so i don't put
                   them anymore ...

V0.31: Bug Fix:	Can now unarc into any dir...
		"Ram Disk:" and "spaced name" now works everywhere!
		aski added in guide :)
                it's finally on Aminet... 

V0.3 : Replace Tooltype routine by AFC one. (Much better!!)
       Remove enforcer hit when cleaning Exec list.
       Read the arguments when :
		Started from Toolmanager or Wb (shift-select)
		Started from Cli or via Lha/Lzx DefIcon 

V0.2 : Lot of bug removed...
       A MWB icon and a Guide :)
       'Show' now work fine with Multiview !!!
       It's localized !
       Added Iconify option and an Appicon when iconified.
       Added prefs in tooltypes (source, destination & appicon path)
       Got new enforcer hit and some new bugs too...

V0.1 : First version (No V0.01 or else :)
       After 2 weeks of hard developing, it looks to work fine, exept 'show'.
       Still some bugs...



There is some known bugs:
 - it can't work with archives with more than 2000 files...
          Well, it isn't really a bug because it's the size of my array.
 - Sometimes, it unarc selected files in "sys:" (!?!?...strange) 

Others, but not my fault:
 - askiz looks very bad with Multiview :(
 - can't delete protected files in T:
 - `shrink' method not supported by unzip (u get "erreur code 81" in a shell)
 - untgz can't extract selected files.

If you still find any other bug or some enforcer hits, just send @{"me" link author} an e-mail
@ENDNODE
